data.description: Charming Home with Modern Upgrades in Bowie, MD Welcome to 1801 Packer Ct, Bowie, MD 20716 – a beautifully renovated home that combines classic charm with modern amenities. This residence boasts numerous upgrades, making it an ideal place for comfortable and contemporary living. Property Details: Address: 1801 Packer Ct, Bowie, MD 20716 Bedrooms: 3 Bathrooms: 2 Key Features: New Roof: Enjoy peace of mind with a brand-new roof that provides both durability and aesthetic appeal. New HVAC System: Stay comfortable year-round with a state-of-the-art heating, ventilation, and air conditioning system. New Electronic Panel: The latest in electrical technology ensures the safety and efficiency of your home's power supply. Wood Flooring: Elegant wood flooring adds warmth and sophistication to the living spaces. Ceramic Tiles: Stylish ceramic tiles adorn the bathrooms and kitchen, providing both durability and easy maintenance. Updated Stainless Steel Appliances: The kitchen is equipped with modern stainless steel appliances, combining functionality with a sleek design. New Refrigerator: A brand-new refrigerator adds convenience and enhances the kitchen's overall appeal. New Washer and Dryer: Enjoy the convenience of a new washer and dryer, making laundry a breeze. Additional Features: Spacious and well-lit interiors. Ample storage space throughout the home. Freshly painted walls in neutral tones, ready for your personal touch. Landscaped backyard with the potential for outdoor entertaining. Location: Conveniently located in Bowie, MD, this home offers easy access to local amenities, schools, parks, and major transportation routes like 50,301, and The Beltway. This property is located in a bank-designated census tract and qualifies for Home Access  -  $10,000 lender credit.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this turnkey property that seamlessly combines modern updates with classic charm. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and make 1801 Packer Ct your new home!
